1
00:00:50,910 --> 00:00:54,000
Your Majesty, the entire Chen family has been fiercely loyal,

2
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:56,080
guarding the rivers and mountains of Dayong for generations.

3
00:00:56,080 --> 00:00:57,910
Her Grace the Empress was innocent,

4
00:00:57,910 --> 00:00:59,580
and His Highness the Crown Prince died a wrongful death.

5
00:00:59,580 --> 00:01:01,540
I beg Your Majesty to clear the Chen family's name,

6
00:01:01,540 --> 00:01:04,540
and bring justice to the Empress and the Crown Prince.

7
00:01:07,790 --> 00:01:10,250
Your Majesty, the evidence is irrefutable.

8
00:01:11,250 --> 00:01:13,910
I entreat Your Majesty to clear the Chen family's name,

9
00:01:13,910 --> 00:01:15,660
give the Empress and the Crown Prince a proper burial,

10
00:01:15,660 --> 00:01:17,590
and give the world an explanation.

11
00:01:23,789 --> 00:01:24,590
Your Majesty.

12
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:27,090
Lin Jingyuan is absolutely right.

13
00:01:27,700 --> 00:01:29,330
The Chen family has been loyal for generations,

14
00:01:29,330 --> 00:01:31,539
and the Empress was virtuous and gentle.

15
00:01:31,539 --> 00:01:33,750
I implore Your Majesty to investigate this matter thoroughly,

16
00:01:33,750 --> 00:01:35,330
restore the innocence of the loyal,

17
00:01:35,330 --> 00:01:38,160
and set the minds of the court and the people at ease.

18
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:40,250
Your Majesty, I humbly make bold to say,

19
00:01:40,250 --> 00:01:43,289
this witch used illusions to deceive the two officials,

20
00:01:43,289 --> 00:01:45,500
fabricating images to slander the royal family.

21
00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:47,759
Keeping her will surely bring disaster.

22
00:02:04,290 --> 00:02:07,330
Insolent! A eunuch dares to spread rumors here?

23
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:08,580
The evidence is clear.

24
00:02:08,580 --> 00:02:10,250
How dare you turn black into white?

25
00:02:10,250 --> 00:02:11,160
What are your intentions?

26
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,160
Calm your anger, Your Majesty.

27
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,450
Jingchen is young and impulsive,

28
00:02:13,450 --> 00:02:14,580
and lost his sense of propriety for a moment.

29
00:02:14,580 --> 00:02:16,290
I hope Your Majesty can forgive him.

30
00:02:16,290 --> 00:02:17,579
Jingchen is loyal to the emperor and loves his country,

31
00:02:17,579 --> 00:02:19,370
and has no treasonous intentions.

32
00:02:19,370 --> 00:02:21,900
I hope Your Majesty can investigate clearly.

33
00:02:29,660 --> 00:02:30,500
However, Your Majesty,

34
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:32,329
the art of yin and yang is too profound,

35
00:02:32,329 --> 00:02:35,040
not easily comprehended by ordinary people like us.

36
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:37,579
The images today ultimately came from this Soul Lamp,

37
00:02:37,579 --> 00:02:38,500
making it difficult to distinguish truth from falsehood.

38
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:41,000
Why not ask the Lantern Lady to temporarily seal the Soul Lamp,

39
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,450
and move it to the side hall for safekeeping,

40
00:02:42,450 --> 00:02:43,910
until we have thoroughly investigated this matter,

41
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:45,310
and then make a decision.

42
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:49,880
Your Majesty,

43
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:52,550
the Prime Minister is merciful,

44
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:56,500
but this witch's evil arts are a menace if kept.

45
00:02:57,329 --> 00:02:59,540
Your Majesty must not be soft-hearted.

46
00:02:59,870 --> 00:03:01,930
Using evil arts to confuse the public

47
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,750
and slander the royal family.

48
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,080
Imperial Guards, hear my command!

49
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:08,080
Capture this witch and her accomplices immediately!

50
00:03:08,160 --> 00:03:09,160
Do not fail.

51
00:03:27,410 --> 00:03:30,010
Xie Jingchen, there are ambushers on the left.

52
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,010
Get on the horse.

53
00:04:42,409 --> 00:04:43,830
As long as she is fine.

54
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:46,790
You just had to take this sword attack head-on.

55
00:04:46,790 --> 00:04:47,909
Half an inch deeper,

56
00:04:47,909 --> 00:04:50,370
and your meridians would have been severed.

57
00:04:55,830 --> 00:04:56,620
A-Deng.

58
00:04:57,330 --> 00:04:59,290
Don't you feel something is wrong with Qin Chong?

59
00:04:59,290 --> 00:05:00,580
In the court today,

60
00:05:00,580 --> 00:05:02,500
he seemed to defend us at every turn,

61
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:04,540
but in reality, every word was handing a knife to the Emperor.

62
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:05,910
It looked like he was being thorough,

63
00:05:05,910 --> 00:05:07,790
but he was actually giving the Emperor a legitimate excuse

64
00:05:07,790 --> 00:05:09,540
to capture us and take away the Soul Lamp.

65
00:05:09,540 --> 00:05:11,580
If the Emperor hadn't directly decided to kill us,

66
00:05:11,580 --> 00:05:14,620
this set of arguments alone would have forced us into a dead end.

67
00:05:14,620 --> 00:05:15,750
And Eunuch Lin.

68
00:05:16,410 --> 00:05:18,580
Eunuch Lin jumped out twice to frame you,

69
00:05:18,580 --> 00:05:20,500
and Qin Chong exchanged glances with him both times.

70
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:22,750
That old man looks respectable on the surface,

71
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:25,160
but he's actually in cahoots with this eunuch.

72
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,500
They played us all.

73
00:05:31,410 --> 00:05:32,330
Enemy attack!

74
00:05:37,330 --> 00:05:38,620
General, bad news!

75
00:05:38,790 --> 00:05:43,920
The Imperial Guard commander has surrounded the general's manor with thousands of troops.

76
00:05:48,159 --> 00:05:50,620
The private soldiers in my manor can hold them off for a while.

77
00:05:50,620 --> 00:05:52,409
There's a secret passage in the west of the manor leading straight out of the city.

78
00:05:52,409 --> 00:05:54,740
I'll take you through the secret passage.

79
00:05:56,580 --> 00:05:57,700
It's too late.

80
00:06:05,290 --> 00:06:06,330
She's here.

81
00:06:09,330 --> 00:06:11,620
Now you've been driven to a dead end by that vile emperor,

82
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:12,950
and have nowhere to run.

83
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,620
Do you want to cooperate with me?

84
00:06:14,620 --> 00:06:17,350
I can help you kill that ungrateful vile emperor.

85
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:19,910
I can even help you protect the people around you.

86
00:06:19,910 --> 00:06:21,200
But you must tell me,

87
00:06:21,330 --> 00:06:23,700
why you abandoned me back then.

88
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,750
Xie Jingchen colluded with evil spirits

89
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:32,909
and used dark magic to murder

90
00:06:32,909 --> 00:06:33,950
and frame the loyal.

91
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:34,830
He deserves death.

92
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:35,750
His Majesty has decreed:

93
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:36,950
Capture Xie Jingchen alive!

94
00:06:36,950 --> 00:06:39,000
Attack! Break the door open!
